data.description: This charming five bedroom home with one bedroom on the entry level is nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this home promises ample space and boasts vaulted ceilings. Discover the additional features that make this property truly special: two cozy fireplaces for warmth and ambiance, dual dining rooms perfect for entertaining, elegant French doors connecting indoor and outdoor living, no front neighbors for added privacy, convenient freeway access making your daily commute a breeze, a covered patio for year-round outdoor enjoyment, turf and low-maintenance yards for stress-free living, a balcony off the primary suite providing a tranquil space for morning coffee or stargazing at night, and a low HOA that comes with a RV / Boat storage lot .warmth and ambiance, dual dining rooms perfect for entertaining, elegant French doors connecting indoor and outdoor living, no front neighbors for added privacy, convenient freeway access making your daily commute a breeze, a covered patio for year-round outdoor enjoyment, turf and low-maintenance yards for stress-free living, a balcony off the primary suite providing a tranquil space for morning coffee or stargazing at night, and a low HOA that comes with a RV / Boat storage lot .
